info.description:
==================
Omnivore Framework
==================



Abstract
========

This is the framework component for Omnivore. This isn't really useful by
itself, but as a convenient pip dependency that includes the specific forked
versions of dependencies for those changes that haven't yet been included in
the upstream projects.
